          h1 Machine Translation
        section
          h2 History of Machine Translation
          ul
            li 1954 Georgetown-IBM experiment
            li 1966 ALPAC report
            li 1970s-1980s: Rule-based MT
            li 1993 Statistical MT (IBM/Brown)
            li 2000s: Statistical MT (Och/Koehn)
            li 2014 Neural MT (Google)
        section(data-background-image="img/google_translate.png" data-background-opacity=0.5)
