                td(style="width:6em") 堂兄 / 堂哥
                td elder
                td father's brother's son
                td(style="width:6em")  表兄 /  表哥
                td elder
                td mother's sibling's or father's sister's son
              tr
                td  堂弟
                td younger
                td father's brother's son
                td  表弟
                td younger
                td mother's sibling's or father's sister's son
              tr
                td  堂姐 / 堂姊
                td elder
                td father's brother's daughter
                td  表姐 /  表姊
                td elder
                td mother's sibling's or father's sister's daughter
              tr
                td  堂妹
                td younger
                td father's brother's daughter
                td  表妹
                td younger
                td mother's sibling's or father's sister's daughter
        section
          h1 Buzz Group
          p Why is translation hard in your language?
        section
          h2 Under-resourced Languages
          div(style="width:40%;float:left")
